  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nWhen specifying the `--enr-address` flag, `--enr-tcp-port` defaults to `--port` when not set, however, `--enr-udp-port` does not. Meaning, if you specify `--enr-address` and don't specify `--enr-udp-port` the beacon chain process will not run.\r\n\r\nI think it make sense to default to port here.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n```\r\nsigp/lighthouse:latest\r\nDIGEST:sha256:ad23d728888e11ae1e348c69cae1a6f228af5286f803400ec60f0fa9c052d12a\r\n```\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nenr-udp-port does not default to port when not specified\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nenr-udp-port defaults to port when not specified\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nset `--enr-udp-port=9000`\r\n",
