    "body": "Thank you for the detailed response...\r\n\r\nSo coming from Prysm and Geth, they both have flags to advertise your external IP such as `--nat` on Geth, `--p2p-host-ip` and `--p2p-host-dns` on Prysm...so I assumed that this was the equivalent.\r\n\r\nBut it sounds like it's not? Is there an alternative, or is it really just better to let it dynamically figure it out?",
