    "body": "This is correct. \r\n\r\nDynamic discovery should set this up automatically for you in < 30 seconds. You can tell by the info log \"Address Updated\". \r\n\r\nIf you for some reason get these settings wrong, you will be adding a non-contactable node to the DHT, which can linger for a while, degrading discovery. ",
